No. 10-10624. Thomas Davis, Petitioner v. Allegheny County, Pennsylvania, et al. 565 U.S. 803, 132 S. Ct. 373, 2011 U.S. LEXIS 7031.

181 L. Ed. 2d 4,

October 3, 2011.
